      • EXE_PREFIX

        public static final String EXE_PREFIX
        Prefix used in several Config String properties. "exe."
        These properties are used to give the path to executables. Unlike most file path properties, they are not converted from host-path style when using a docker container; thus, an ""exe."" property can be used to specify an executable within a docker container. In contrast, the "hostExe." prefix is used the same way, but it is translated to allow an in-container script to use the host file path specified.
